description:
hides all the "hidden" answers and the ads in the middle that push the real answers way down the page;
hides the right sidebar, and top ad banner; 
makes the main content area take up the whole width (replacing the right sidebar);
hides the BIG tabs in the page header; 
tightens up the page header, height-wise, to take up less room;

css:
@namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);

@-moz-document domain("experts-exchange.com") {
  #EchoTopic .startFreeTrial, .sectionFour, .ontopBanner, .questionStats, 
  .question .answers, #pageRight, #compPgHrNav, #compDt, .squareSignUp, 
  .notFreePAQ, #zoneAdvertisment {
    display: none !important;
  }

  #pageHeader {
    height: 96px !important;
  }

  #compZnNav {
    top: 75px !important;
  }

  #breadCrumb {
    padding-top: 3px !important;
    padding-bottom: 3px !important;
  }

  #pageMain {
    width: 935px !important;
  }
}
